---
import DefaultLayout from "../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro";
---

<DefaultLayout title="Welcome">
    <main>

 <!--       <header class="flex items-center justify-center h-screen pb-12">
            <div class="content bg-base-100 mx-4 p-4 text-center md:p-8">
                <h1 class="mb-6 text-xl md:text-5xl">we are the dreamers, and we are the believers</h1>
            </div>
        </header>
  -->   

  <!-- Section 1 - Introduction -->
        <div class="bg-section1 flex items-center justify-center h-screen mx-4">
            <div class="card glass lg:card-side text-neutral-content">
                <div class="max-w-md card-body content items-center justify-center">
                    <h1>we are the dreamers, and we are the believers</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content leading-normal mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-lg">
            <h2>The future of space exploration is here!</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">We believe in a world where anyone can access space, and we're making it happen.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">We are revolutionising the space industry by streamlining the regulatory process and making it easier for companies to access space. Our mission is to enable the world to explore and utilise space to its fullest potential. Are you ready to take your company to new heights? Let us help you get there.</p>
            <div class="card-actions items-center justify-center">
                <button class="btn glass rounded-full">Get Started</button>
            </div>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
    

        <!-- Section 2 - The problem-->
        <div class="bg-section2 flex items-center justify-center h-screen mx-4">
            <div class="card glass lg:card-side text-neutral-content">
                <div class="max-w-md card-body content items-center justify-center">
                    <h1>we recombobulate</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content leading-normal mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-lg">
            <h2>we create clarity from confusion</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Getting access to space is a complex and often frustrating process. The regulatory requirements are confusing, time-consuming, expensive, and can be difficult to navigate, requiring extensive knowledge and resources.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">This is a major barrier for companies wanting to reach for the stars, and can limit innovation and progress in the industry.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">That's where we come in.</p>
            <div class="card-actions items-center justify-center">
                <button class="btn glass rounded-full">Get Started</button>
            </div>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>


        <!-- Section 3 - The solution-->
        <div class="bg-section3 flex items-center justify-center h-screen mx-4">
            <div class="card glass lg:card-side text-neutral-content">
                <div class="max-w-md card-body content items-center justify-center">
                    <h1>we see some red tape and we want to paint it black</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content leading-normal mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-lg">
            <h2>we simplify the mess</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">At Blue Dwarf Space, we have developed a platform that streamlines the regulatory process and makes it easier for companies to apply for and track space activity permits.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Our platform guides you through the entire process, from initial application to final approval.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">We provide you with all the necessary information, resources, and support you need to successfully apply for and obtain space activity permits.</p>
            <div class="card-actions items-center justify-center">
                <button class="btn glass rounded-full">Get Started</button>
            </div>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>


        <!-- Section 4 - How -->

        <div class="bg-section4 flex items-center justify-center h-screen mx-4">
            <div class="card glass lg:card-side text-neutral-content">
                <div class="max-w-md card-body content items-center justify-center">
                    <h1>We are here to help</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content leading-normal mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-lg">
            <h2>your one-stop regulatory shop</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Our platform provides a centralized hub for all regulatory requirements, allowing companies to easily apply for permits and track the progress of their applications.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">We also provide educational resources and support to help companies navigate the complex regulatory landscape.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">If your company is launching a rocket, our platform also enables your partnering companies who have payloads on that rocket to have their products approved for your mission.</p>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">With our help, you can launch your rockets, send satellites into orbit, and achieve your space exploration goals. We take on the busy work so that you can concentrate on what you do best: awesome space stuff!</p>
            <div class="card-actions items-center justify-center">
                <button class="btn glass rounded-full">Get Started</button>
            </div>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>


        <!-- Section 5 - Come on then, what are you waiting for? -->

        <div class="bg-section5 flex items-center justify-center h-screen mx-4">
            <div class="card glass lg:card-side text-neutral-content">
                <div class="max-w-md card-body content items-center justify-center">
                    <h1>join the space revolution</h1>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Become part of a new generation of space explorers today by signing up with Blue Dwarf Space.</p>
                    <div class="card-actions items-center justify-center">
                        <button class="btn glass rounded-full">Get Started</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content leading-normal mx-auto py-12 px-4 max-w-lg">
            <h2>Get in touch!</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">Our platform is designed to meet the needs of individuals and companies of all sizes. Whether you're an established aerospace company or a new space startup, we're here to help you reach the stars. Get started today and take the first step towards your space mission with Blue Dwarf Space.</p>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</DefaultLayout>


